glosses.gloss: Aqualung is the fourth studio album by the rock band Jethro Tull.
A scuba set is any breathing apparatus that is carried entirely by an underwater diver and provides the diver with breathing gas at the ambient pressure.

Matt Hales is an English songwriter, musician, and record producer who has been performing professionally under the name Aqualung since the early 2000s.
Stage name of British musician Matt Hales
"Aqualung" is a song by the British progressive rock band Jethro Tull, and the title track from their Aqualung album.
A device (trade name Aqua-Lung) that lets divers breathe under water; scuba is an acronym for self-contained underwater breathing apparatus
A piece of equipment consisting of an oxygen tank and breathing apparatus used by divers to allow them to breathe underwater at depth.
